data.description: Stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home nestled in charming Charleston-themed community. You’ll be captivated by the fully covered front porch, inviting relaxation. Fenced private backyard complete with a cobblestone patio with a large outdoor fireplace nook for grilling, perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends. California-style master closet, whole house built-in sound system with ceiling speakers allows you to create a harmonious atmosphere. Whole house water purification system, new Energy-efficient HVAC system, new water heater, Custom-built backyard storage shed, large windows throughout the house allow natural sunlight to flood each room, beautiful custom molding throughout. Granite kitchen countertops provide both durability and style. The master bathroom boasts a large, deep jacuzzi tub with jets, offering a luxurious retreat. Top-rated elementary and middle school district.
